name: Amulets
description:
Do you have a Amulet/Talisman for Protection ?

"A amulet or talisman is something thought to be imbued with some magical property. It can both protect, and radiate power, and is often used in ritual."

Historically in every culture, Talismans, and Amulets are used to ward away curses, hexes and the evil eye. One of the most powerful forms of Voodoo and African magic is the amulet or talisman. This can be used to attract love, life, health, economic well-being and all types of benefit. Moreover, once consecrated, the amulet can be used to protect from spiritual predators and any kind of damage used by opposing dark Voodoo forces.
